<body>
    <div class="home-main">
        <div class="gradient"></div>
        <img class="home-bg" src="/media/background.jpg" alt="Desk in front of a wall" />
        <div class="home-overlay">
            <header>
                <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm navbar-toggleable-sm mb-3">
                    <div class="container-fluid">
                        <a class="navbar-brand" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index"><img src="data:," class="home-logo" alt="Devpendent Logo" /></a>
                        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target=".navbar-collapse" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent"
                                aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="30" height="21" viewBox="0 0 30 21">
                                    <g transform="translate(-3 -7.5)">
                                        <path d="M4.5,18h27" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" />
                                        <path d="M4.5,9h27" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" />
                                        <path d="M4.5,27h27" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" />
                                    </g>
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                        </button>
                        <div id="navbarSupportedContent" class="navbar-collapse collapse d-sm-inline-flex justify-content-end">
                            <ul class="navbar-nav">
                                <li class="nav-item">
                                    <a class="nav-link text-white" asp-area="" asp-controller="Projects" asp-action="Index">Browse</a>
                                </li>
                                <partial name="_HomeLoginPartial" />
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </nav>
            </header>
            <div class="home-text">
                <h1 class="home-title">Hire freelance developers on your own terms</h1>
                <p class="home-desc">
                    Devpendent is a web service dedicated to helping developers with finding freelance work. The website acts as a place for these developers to post the work they offer and create a profile with their qualifications so employers can find them. At the same time Devpendent also acts as a place for these employers to find skilled and dedicated freelance developers to help bring their projects to life. As an employer you can browse our many categories for jobs as well as search for specific jobs to find exactly the developer or job you are looking for.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <main>
            <partial name="_NotificationPartial" />
            <div class="row">
                @RenderBody()
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>

